               ISO8601-like (or RFC 3339-like) format.
       
               Use a style parameter of '%', '{' or '$' to specify that you want to
               use one of %-formatting, :meth:`str.format` (``{}``) formatting or
               :class:`string.Template` formatting in your format string.
       
